<div class="card">
  <h1 class="title is-1 center"><u>{{oneRecipe.title}}:</u></h1>
  <div class="columns">
    <div class="column center">
      <div class="card-image recipes-image">
        <figure class="image">
          <img src="{{oneRecipe.image}}" alt="Placeholder image">
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="column">
      <div class="card-content">
        <nav class="level is-mobile level-right">
          <div class="level-left">
            <a class="level-item" aria-label="reply">
              <span class="icon is-medium">
                <i class="fas fa-2x fa-reply icon-reply" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              </span>
            </a>
            <a class="level-item" aria-label="retweet">
              <span class="icon is-medium">
                <i class="fas fa-2x fa-retweet icon-retweet" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              </span>
            </a>
            <a class="level-item" aria-label="like" href="/add-fav-recipe/{{oneRecipe._id}}"> <span
                class="icon is-medium">
                <i class="fas fa-2x fa-heart icon-like" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              </span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </nav>


        <div class="media">
          <div class="media-content recipe-list">
            <div class="card-content">
              <div class="columns" style="display: flex;align-items: baseline;">
                <div class="column">
                  <span class="icon is-large">
                    <i class="fas fa-stopwatch fa-2x"></i>
                  </span>
                  <p class="is-size-5 has-text-centered"> {{oneRecipe.cookingTime}} min. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="column">
                  <span class="icon is-large">
                    <i class="fas fa-hourglass-half fa-2x"></i>
                  </span>
                  <p class="is-size-5 has-text-centered"> {{oneRecipe.prepTime}} min. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="column">
                  <p class="is-size-4 has-text-centered"> {{oneRecipe.kCal}} kCal </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <footer class="card-footer">
              <p class="card-footer-item has-background-primary"> P{{oneRecipe.protein}} </p>
              <p class="card-footer-item has-background-warning"> C{{oneRecipe.carbs}} </p>
              <p class="card-footer-item has-background-light"> L{{oneRecipe.lipid}} </p>
            </footer>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="columns">
    <div class="column is-one-third">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="title is-4"> &nbsp; What you need:</p>
        <ul>
          {{#each oneRecipe.ingredientList}}
          <li>{{this}}</li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="is-divider-vertical"></div>
    <div class="column">
      <p class="title is-4">Let's cook:</p>
      <p>Post hanc adclinis Libano monti Phoenice, regio plena gratiarum et venustatis, urbibus decorata magnis et
        pulchris; in quibus amoenitate celebritateque nominum Tyros excellit, Sidon et Berytus isdemque pares Emissa et
        Damascus saeculis condita priscis.

        Sed quid est quod in hac causa maxime homines admirentur et reprehendant meum consilium, cum ego idem antea
        multa
        decreverim, que magis ad hominis dignitatem quam ad rei publicae necessitatem pertinerent? Supplicationem
        quindecim dierum decrevi sententia mea. Rei publicae satis erat tot dierum quot C. Mario ; dis immortalibus non
        erat exigua eadem gratulatio quae ex maximis bellis. Ergo ille cumulus dierum hominis est dignitati tributus.

        Ciliciam vero, quae Cydno amni exultat, Tarsus nobilitat, urbs perspicabilis hanc condidisse Perseus memoratur,
        Iovis filius et Danaes, vel certe ex Aethiopia profectus Sandan quidam nomine vir opulentus et nobilis et
        Anazarbus auctoris vocabulum referens, et Mopsuestia vatis illius domicilium Mopsi, quem a conmilitio
        Argonautarum
        cum aureo vellere direpto redirent, errore abstractum delatumque ad Africae litus mors repentina consumpsit, et
        ex
        eo cespite punico tecti manes eius heroici dolorum varietati medentur plerumque sospitales.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>